text: Mitrofanovka () is a rural locality (a selo) in Mikhaylovsky Selsoviet, Duvansky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 207 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 31 km from Mesyagutovo, 6 km from Mikhaylovka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Duvansky District
title: Mitrofanovka
